
"use Bailador" gives you exported subs like get(), post(), etc.  See hello.p6 
for example.

But the docs say that there are newer features that require you to make your 
app a class that inherits from Bailador::App.  See ./simple_inherit.p6 for 
example.


basic/ {
    This is still meant to be a very basic app, while showing more of the 
    features of bailador.
}

